Priority: extra
Maintainer: Daron Chabot <dchabot@bnl.gov>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 7), autotools-dev
Standards-Version: 3.8.3
Homepage: http://www.gmca.aps.anl.gov/TPMAC2/

Package: tpmac
Architecture: any
Depends: epics-synapps (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Libraries for working with Delta Tau Turbo PMACs.
 tpmac contains the libraries and database defintions files for
 working with Delta Tau Turbo PMAC boards in an EPICS developement
 environment. This is a stripped down version containing only the 
 support developed at Diamond Light Source.
 .
 This package contains support for network/serial-based PMACs.
